
Overview of noun slave

The noun slave has 3 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                          
1. (18) slave -- (a person who is owned by someone)
2. (1) slave, striver, hard worker -- (someone who works as hard as a slave)
3. slave -- (someone entirely dominated by some influence or person; "a slave to fashion"; "a slave to cocaine"; "his mother was his abject slave")

